      <title>由于未能达成协议，英国与加拿大的贸易壁垒增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-canada-trade-barriers-to-increase-amid-failure-to-reach-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国未能就延期达成协议后，允许英国向加拿大免税销售含有欧盟零部件的产品的规定将于周一到期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-canada-trade-barriers-to-increase-amid-failure-to-reach-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾在中美争端中改造海事安全办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/philippines-revamps-maritime-security-offices-amid-china-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着与北京的南海紧张局势升级，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯重组了中央海上安全政策机构的职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/philippines-revamps-maritime-security-offices-amid-china-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其城市地方选举中面临激烈竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 及其执政党在周日的地方选举中陷入了激烈的竞争，这是在赢得新任期 10 个月后对领导人权力的关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克和斯塔默发布复活节信息，关注即将到来的选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/sunak-and-starmer-issue-easter-messages-with-eye-on-election-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）表示，复活节是一个“暂停和反思”的时刻，而工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默爵士（Sir Keir Starmer）则表示，这是一个“乐观和新开始”的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/sunak-and-starmer-issue-easter-messages-with-eye-on-election-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 22:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>主要民意调查显示，保守党将迎来最糟糕的选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/tories-set-for-worst-election-result-major-poll-suggests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党议员在大选中可能会减少到不到 100 名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/tories-set-for-worst-election-result-major-poll-suggests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 19:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
