    <item>
      <title>联合国观察员在黎巴嫩南部巡逻时发生爆炸受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/4-un-military-observers-wounded-in-an-explosion-while-patrolling-lebanon-s-southern-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝鲁特（美联社）——联合国驻黎巴嫩维和特派团表示，周六，三名联合国军事观察员和一名黎巴嫩翻译在黎巴嫩南部边境巡逻时，一枚炮弹在他们附近爆炸，导致他们受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/4-un-military-observers-wounded-in-an-explosion-while-patrolling-lebanon-s-southern-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 11:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对饥饿的担忧加剧，载有援助物资的船只前往加沙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/the-us-welcomes-the-new-palestinian-government-following-its-repeated-calls-for-political-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——由于人们对加沙地区饥饿问题的担忧加剧，一支由三艘船组成的船队于周六离开塞浦路斯的一个港口，向加沙运送了 400 吨食品和其他物资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/the-us-welcomes-the-new-palestinian-government-following-its-repeated-calls-for-political-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 08:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在倒塌的桥梁上，重点转向拆除大型结构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/at-collapsed-baltimore-bridge-focus-shifts-to-the-weighty-job-of-removing-the-massive-structure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴尔的摩（美联社）——周六，工程师团队在复杂的过程中，从倒塌的弗朗西斯·斯科特基桥上切割和吊起第一段扭曲的钢材。本周，一艘巨大的货船撞上了桥的一个支架，这座桥陷入了帕塔普斯科河。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/at-collapsed-baltimore-bridge-focus-shifts-to-the-weighty-job-of-removing-the-massive-structure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 04:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
